{"tid":921294,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地每年交咁多稅, 班公務員食左屎?","createTime":"2018-11-29T12:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T02:25:29.000Z","uid":204309,"like":16,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ceb0951f7347894b22cc6f1abd509c0ab27a53","tid":921294,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇東張西望, 有人投訴豬場扔就死既活豬去垃圾站, 街坊投訴極都係比漁護署hea覆, 根本無諗住做野<br />\n我地每年辛苦賺埋既, 要交稅去養班食到肚滿腸肥, lunch後就返office睇報紙吹水既公務員, 呢班廢物每日就係返去做例行公事, 完全無諗過出面社會發生緊咩事, 可以做咩去改善做得更好<br />\n但就攞住高人工, 無論上至下級一律都係<br />\n識好多返公司睇馬經, 一日夾埋吹幾粒鐘水既公務員, 唔使望係講緊你, 有機會實係office影低你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再係咁真係唔想交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b28df22bebd9e033fa5de393f998281cff03243","tid":921294,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"多謝東張西望喎"},{"pid":"a26805bad5cbb7d9c645de5b5eb9d68789c7e25b","tid":921294,"uid":64855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"唔好交囉"},{"pid":"1aa6896e7c215abc0d8558e3de356c1235b5fd9e","tid":921294,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"乜有人會想交稅㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22b2d883adb1b32e43949c18c258b8cd8a32f37","tid":921294,"uid":118709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"做政府做又36唔做又36<br />\n年年跳point 加人工，房屋津貼<br />\n<br />\n理撚得你"},{"pid":"883e6aa17f1a375b013903a2e738c1bd19c95aad","tid":921294,"uid":35420,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"你交幾多咁巴閉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709f259b2b073b99040b9c4cd827345b0d3b1a0b","tid":921294,"uid":13108,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"